### Login as Alice
POST http://localhost:8000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "alice@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Login as Bob
POST http://localhost:8000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "bob@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Read Acme document
GET http://localhost:8000/documents/aaaaaaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaaaaaaaaaa
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Edit Acme document
PATCH http://localhost:8000/documents/aaaaaaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaaaaaaaaaa
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Acme Plan"
}

### Share Acme document
POST http://localhost:8000/documents/aaaaaaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaaaaaaaaaa/shares
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "subject_type": "user",
  "subject_id": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002",
  "role": "viewer"
}

### Revoke Acme document share
DELETE http://localhost:8000/documents/aaaaaaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaaaaaaaaaa/shares
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "subject_type": "user",
  "subject_id": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002",
  "role": "viewer"
}

### Create delegated link
POST http://localhost:8000/documents/aaaaaaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaaaaaaaaaa/shares/delegated-link
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "expires_in_seconds": 300
}

### Read delegated document
GET http://localhost:8000/delegated/documents/aaaaaaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaaaaaaaaaa
x-delegation-token: {{delegation_token}}

### Inspect document relationships
GET http://localhost:8000/documents/aaaaaaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaaaaaaaaaa/relationships
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Audit logs
GET http://localhost:8000/audit
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

